          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637061023692-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining sliced red onion</strong> to a medium bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
